Discover!
Windmill Inns
of America
# ASHLAND
HILLS INN
Windmill's Ashland Hills Inn is southern Oregon's
largest meeting and convention inn with 159 queen and
king rooms, plus affordable suites. Free airport pickup
in Medford and Ashland. Free tennis, golf nearby.
free in-room movies, plus new affordable rates.
# MEDFORD
WINDMILL
Free airport shuttle, free in-room movies,
complimentary morning coffee and newspaper to
business travelers, indoor jacuzzi, sauna, heated pool,
restaurant and lounge adjacent.
# ROSEBURG
WINDMILL
Roseburg's most complete motor inn. Free in-room
movies, cable TV, complimentary morning coffee and
newspaper to business travelers, indoor jacuzzi, sauna,
heated pool, plus the brand-new Piper Café
and Sandpiper dinner house.
Discover the Growing Family of
Windmill Inns - All our Inns feature free use
of ten speed bikes, best selling novels from
the Windmill Library, free Showtime in-room
movies, and a warm Windmill welcome.
In Oregon: 1-800-452-5315
Outside Oregon: 1-800-547-4747
